### Get all Posts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/posts HTTP/1.1

### Get Post by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/posts/:1 HTTP/1.1

### Post new Post
POST  http://localhost:3000/api/posts/new HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "name": "Item 1", 
     "description": "hello"
}

### Update Post by ID
PUT  http://localhost:3000/api/posts/edit/:1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
     
     "name": "Item 1", 
     "description": "helloo"
}

### Delete Post by ID
DELETE   http://localhost:3000/api/posts/delete/:1 HTTP/1.1